equities); Pounds 25,000 (managed fund portfolio service)
Current asset allocation for private clients: 61%; overseas equities
19%; bonds, 19%; cash, 1%
Average annual portfolio turnover: 25-30%
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Fees: 0.6% on first Pounds 500,000, 0.3% next Pounds 500,000 and 0.15%
thereafter (minimum Pounds 750 a year) plus transaction commissions at a
40% discount (discretionary clients); Pounds 250 administration fee plus
transaction commissions ranging from 1.85% to 0.3% (advisory clients)
